    ('cat_board_books', 9, 9, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for bounce along rhyme', 'Hairy Maclary and Zachary Quack', 'Puffin', 'LoveReading4Kids', 'https://www.lovereading4kids.co.uk/book/9780141381138/isbn/Hairy-Maclary-and-Zachary-Quack-by-Lynley-Dodd.html', NULL, 'See retailer', 'in_stock', 'Baby and toddler', 'Lynley Dodd Hairy Maclary and Zachary Quack board book with bouncing rhyme and animal friends to point out together on sturdy pages.', 'Rhythm carries a longer listen than a single picture page. Use it when they are settled on your chest and ready for a short story pulse. Keep one verse, then stop while the listen still feels friendly rather than pushing a full chapter.', 'Shared looking and early chat at 4-6m.', 'Supervise; boards can get chewed.', 'buy', true, 'Good gift if library copy not already loved.', 'Families often own several board books already - ask first.', 'Awake shared reading only; not for the cot.', 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'none'),
