    ('cat_highchair', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for budget wipe-clean', 'IKEA ANTILOP Highchair seat shell', 'IKEA', 'IKEA UK', 'https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/p/antilop-seat-shell-for-highchair-70279942/', NULL, 'Shell + legs + tray ≈ £15–25', 'in_stock', 'Able to sit unaided; up to 3 years / 15 kg', 'The IKEA ANTILOP highchair seat shell, completed with separate legs and tray, giving a simple wipe-clean seat once sitting without help is reliable.', 'First tastes are getting close, but the chair only belongs when sitting is steady without help. ANTILOP keeps cleanup honest for porridge experiments. Budget for legs and tray as well as the shell on the same trip so you leave with a usable seat.', 'Simple supportive seat for early meals.', 'Needs legs+tray; from sitting unaided (~6m).', 'buy', false, 'Parent buy.', 'One highchair usually enough.', 'Only once sitting unaided; harness on; never leave alone.', 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_age_fit'),
