    ('cat_highchair', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for design table seat', 'Bugaboo Giraffe High Chair', 'Bugaboo', 'Boots UK', 'https://www.boots.com/bugaboo-giraffe-high-chair-white-10320750', NULL, 'See Boots', 'in_stock', 'From sitting / highchair use', 'A Bugaboo Giraffe high chair aimed at bringing babies up to the family table with a clean modular frame once sitting is steady.', 'More design led and pricier; only if the look and longevity come ahead of the budget path for a table seat. Confirm Boots stock live before ordering. Ranked last because ANTILOP, Mimzy and Tripp Trapp cover most Conor needs first for early tastes.', 'Table-height supportive seat.', 'Premium price; confirm stock.', 'buy', false, 'Parent buy.', 'One chair.', 'Sitting stage; harness.', 'good', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_url'),
    ('cat_kick_play_socks', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for classic foot finders', 'Lamaze Gardenbug Foot Finder and Wrist Rattle Set', 'Lamaze', 'Hamleys', 'https://www.hamleys.com/lamaze-gardenbug-foot-finder-and-wrist-rattle-set', NULL, '£15.99', 'in_stock', '0–12 months', 'A Lamaze Gardenbug set with soft classic foot finder socks and Velcro wrist rattles that jingle when legs and arms move during supervised floor play.', 'Kicks start making noise on purpose at this age. Soft bug socks stay put so a flail becomes a rattle without needing a precise grab yet. Use on the playmat during nappy changes when feet are already in the air and you can watch the whole time.', 'Cause-and-effect via kicking.', 'Socks can slip off bigger calves; never for sleep.', 'buy', true, 'Popular gift — still useful at 4–6m.', 'Often already owned from newborn gifts.', 'Supervised awake play only; remove for sleep.', 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'none'),
